203
00:09:20,590 --> 00:09:22,870
Tu ferais mieux de me servir.

204
00:09:25,790 --> 00:09:28,570
On dirait que c'est Qin Luan qui veut attraper Chu Chu.

205
00:09:28,570 --> 00:09:30,850
